<h3 id="when-not-to-use-validation-or-error-messages">When not to use validation or error messages</h3>

<p>These messages should only be used to resolve validation issues, they shouldnâ€™t be used to tell users theyâ€™re not eligible for a service. This should be done on a separate screen that gives a way for the user to end or continue their journey.</p>
